{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4747fffef6","title":"关于刘少奇可先回国参加新政协会议致刘少奇、王称祥电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4078041b7d","index":0,"year":1949,"month":7,"day":31,"articleId":"4747fffef6"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"c0db85bbd6","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"阿洛夫，指安德列·雅科夫列维奇·奥尔洛夫，是来中国帮助工作的苏联医生，并担任中共与联共（布）的联络工作。米大夫，指米尔尼柯夫，苏联著名内科医生，1945年12月来中国帮助工作。"},{"id":"80bfa47e7f","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"柯兄，指柯瓦家夫，当时担任来中国帮助工作的苏联专家组负责人。"},{"id":"3b19c2c4a8","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"此处楷体字排印的是周恩来修改时所加的内容。"},{"id":"0829b04f8a","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"AH，毛泽东的代号。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e75083dd8d","type":"title","text":"关于刘少奇可先回国参加新政协会议致刘少奇、王橡祥电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6"},{"id":"c0db85bbd6","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、王：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6"},{"id":"80bfa47e7f","type":"paragraph","text":"午陷各电均悉，答复如下：（一）少奇可先回国，留橡祥在莫斯科，帮助刘亚楼、张学思等接治创办空海两校事完毕，于八月中旬或下句回国一行，参加政协，然后再去苏联。（二）新华社派代表驻莫斯科及塔斯社派代表驻北平，均同意。时间可定在九月政府成立后，人选准备亦要那时才能办好。（三）此外，我认为阿洛夫、来大天叫二人仍以留在中国工作为好，因为他们对中国情况已相当熟悉，他们已学了许多中国话，他们过去的工作是有成绩的，他们的某些缺点是可以改正的，惟他们须统一在村兑领导之下，或留向洛夫而米大夫不再来问，此事是否可行，请与柯兄商的办理","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6"},{"id":"3b19c2c4a8","type":"subtitle","text":"AH","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6"},{"id":"0829b04f8a","type":"paragraph","text":"午世","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6"}],"page":{"id":"732451e23c","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"4747fffef6","start":85,"end":85}}}},"__N_SSG":true}